import React from 'react'
import {
  Drawer,
  DrawerBody,
  DrawerFooter,
  DrawerHeader,
  DrawerOverlay,
  DrawerContent,
  DrawerCloseButton,
  useDisclosure,
  Flex, Box, Spacer, Text, Stack, Radio,RadioGroup
} from "@chakra-ui/react"
import { ArrowBackIcon } from '@chakra-ui/icons'
const ProductCustomizationDrawer = () => {
  const { isOpen, onOpen, onClose } = useDisclosure()
  const [placement, setPlacement] = React.useState("bottom")

  return (
    <Drawer placement={placement} onClose={onClose} isOpen={true}>
      <DrawerOverlay bgColor="rgb(0 0 0 / 78%)" />
      <DrawerContent h='85vh' borderTopRadius='10px' borderTopRightRadius='30px' borderTopLeftRadius="30px">
        <DrawerHeader bg="black" borderTopRightRadius='30px' borderTopLeftRadius="30px">
          <Flex direction="column" mt="16px" mr="33px" mb="12px">
            <Flex>
              <ArrowBackIcon w="20px" alignSelf="flex-end" color="white" />
              <Text ml="10px" color="white" lineHeight="19px" fontSize="16px" fontWeight="bold">{'Mc Aloo tikki'}</Text>
              <Box ml="10px" w="8px" h="8px" mb="10px" border="1px solid #E11010">
                <Box m="0.8px" mt="0.9px" w="4.4px" h="4.4px" bg="#EC1010" />
              </Box>
            </Flex>
            <Text ml="30px" mt="10px" fontSize="14px" lineHeight="17px" fontSize="14px" color="white" >₹{'25'}</Text>
          </Flex>

        </DrawerHeader>
        <DrawerBody>
          <Flex direction="column">
            <Box>
                <Text>SELECT ANY ONE</Text>
              <RadioGroup defaultValue="1">
                <Stack>
                  <Radio value="1" colorScheme="green">Checked </Radio>
                  <Radio value="2" colorScheme="green">Unchecked</Radio>
                  <Radio value="3" colorScheme="green">Unchecked</Radio>
                </Stack>
              </RadioGroup>
            </Box>
          </Flex>
        </DrawerBody>
      </DrawerContent>
    </Drawer>

  )
}

export default ProductCustomizationDrawer
